title: HPI Spencer
content: Walt, a PO1 with carpal tunnel, reports numbness and moderate ecchymosis post-operation. He has minimal pain but seeks resolution of numbness.

title: Musculoskeletal
content: Incision clean, joint sutures, moderate ecchymosis, good finger motion but not full.

title: Plan
content: Post-op endo carpal tunnel; follow-up in 4 weeks.
